<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info {
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        code {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1 style="margin: 0;">üîí Account Locked</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi,</p>

        <p>Your <strong>Munney</strong> account (<code>{{ user.email }}</code>) was locked after 5 failed login attempts.</p>

        <div class="info">
            <strong>Lock Details:</strong><br>
            IP Address: <code>{{ ipAddress }}</code><br>
            Time: <code>{{ user.lockedAt|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}</code> UTC<br>
            Unlock link expires: <code>{{ expiresAt|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}</code> UTC (1 hour)
        </div>

        <p><strong>If this was you:</strong></p>
        <p>Click the button below to unlock your account immediately:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ unlockUrl }}" class="button">Unlock My Account</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
            Or copy this link into your browser:<br>
            <code style="word-break: break-all;">{{ unlockUrl }}</code>
        </p>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è If this wasn't you:</strong><br>
            Someone may be trying to access your account. We recommend:
            <ul style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                <li>Change your password after unlocking</li>
                <li>Enable two-factor authentication (if available)</li>
                <li>Check recent account activity</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 30px;">
            <strong>Note:</strong> After 1 hour, the failed login counter will automatically reset and you can try logging in again (if you remember your password). This unlock link allows you to bypass the wait time.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated security email from Munney.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <strong>Munney Security Team</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
